E4Plus1.uk.title: Made in Chelsea: Thailand
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Tristan, Jules and the gang touch down in Thailand, but there's trouble in paradise when Tristan's ex Molly arrives. In London, Jack and Livvy hit a rough patch. (S30 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bazzini: Award-winning chef Paul runs Italian joint Bazzini in New Jersey, but he didn't realise how difficult running a restaurant would be. Can Gordon turn it around? (S3 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Home Alone 3
E4Plus1.uk.description: (1997) Comedy sequel starring Alex D. Linz as a resourceful boy who's stranded at home with chickenpox when a top-secret military microchip comes his way. Can he keep it safe from crooks?

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Higgs Boson Observation: Amy is jealous when Sheldon hires an attractive female assistant, and Howard's return from space is delayed by a week. (S6 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Re-entry Minimization: Howard is disappointed when he doesn't receive a hero's welcome on his return from space. Will he ever get the recognition he deserves? (S6 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Holographic Excitation: The gang celebrate Halloween with a fancy dress party at Stuart's comic book shop, but Sheldon and Amy can't agree on which costumes to wear. (S6 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Double, Double, Boy in Trouble: Bart switches places with his doppelganger Simon. But it turns out Simon's wealthy family are plotting against him. (S20 Ep3/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Lisa the Drama Queen: Lisa and her new friend Juliet (Emily Blunt) create a fantasy world that takes them a bit too far from reality. (S20 Ep9/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Take My Life, Please: Homer is annoyed when his old high school nemesis Vance Connor gets a spot on the Springfield Walk of Fame. (S20 Ep10/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Mansion Family: Mr Burns leaves town for a full medical check-up, leaving the Simpsons in charge of his mansion. Guest starring Britney Spears as herself. (S11 Ep12/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Saddlesore Galactica: Homer and Bart save a horse from the fair and decide to train him as an American footballer. Or maybe a racehorse. (S11 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Alone Again Natura-Diddily: When tragedy strikes Maude Flanders at Springfield's new race track, the Simpsons must help a bereft Ned. (S11 Ep14/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Missionary: Impossible: Homer pledges $10,000 to save his favourite British sitcom, Do Shut Up. But when the channel comes for the cash, he flees to a South Pacific island. (S11 Ep15/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pygmoelian: After he's snubbed for a Duff beer calendar, Moe goes for plastic surgery and ends up so handsome that he becomes a soap star. (S11 Ep16/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Sister Act
E4Plus1.uk.description: (1992) Comedy starring Whoopi Goldberg. A casino singer who witnesses a Mob murder goes into hiding at a convent, where she soon has the choir rocking. With Maggie Smith.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Celebrity Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: On the Gogglebox this time: First Dates, Squid Game, Olivia Attwood: The Price of Perfection, Match Me Abroad, Building the Band and BBC News (bingo and Oasis). (S7 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to Wrexham, The Good Ship Murder, Married at First Sight UK, Coronation Street and Nadiya's Simple Spices are just some of the great TV shows up for review. (S22 Ep7)
